<plot>Bice is a secretary, Antonella and Mara are models. The three of them are close friends and when they win a million in a lottery, they decide to go to a winter resort to find a rich husband. They steal the new fashions of the fashion house where all of them work and leave Rome. But they are followed by the nephew of the owner of the fashion house.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?361521</url></doc>
